        Ceiling Heights in Brisbane Homes: How Extra Height Changes Buyer Perception and Value
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Ceiling height is one of the strongest indirect signals of property quality, particularly in Brisbane heritage homes. Here is what counts as standard, what counts as premium, and how to market and stage for height.
      </p>
    </div>
